{"tid":1625622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修要提防 做好安全措施","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:01:07.000Z","uid":68686,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2cbb3d76a58f020299c007bf4dd421e1e901c4","tid":1625622,"uid":68686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"相信大家都記得呢一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zQAuzX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zQAuzX.gif&h=d0843a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意到有討論狗狗可能有新部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[警世] 知唔知點解呢兩晚點解班狗遲遲都唔出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1622718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1622718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n要小心尤其係高危嘅商鋪<br />\n褔建360 支那銀行 .etc<br />\n<br />\n可能會有狗狗事先部署好係入面<br />\n一拉開閘門就沖班畜龍岀黎亂槍掃射捉人<br />\n被捉到可能會被告其他有意圖嘅罪行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路過見到有狗部署嘅手捉最好可以影相通知手足<br />\n班狗好陰濕<br />\n可以用運貨嘅方式運裝備同狗隻入鋪部署<br />\n警黑最叻就係合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離有落閘嘅商鋪都要睇清楚有冇上好鎖<br />\n防止有陷阱 有狗沖岀黎就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去開工前都要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推啊 要比前線睇到預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"cae6317943d6f84b54ed905cc31a231d29d752f3","tid":1625622,"uid":257293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論同國際支持<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIO